column5: Actually by my dog... It was creepy...it looked like it was alive, yet not. It's eyes were fixed in a gaze of foreboding doom. Unlike the other 'omen' found in Northern Ontario (which was obviously a mink) this appears to be the real deal....
DANG... she brought home Wiley Coyote...
SNUFFY!!!---You found it---I've been lookin everywhere
Please this is a family community no talk of mounting please!!!
